    "name": "Rahul",
    "age": 24
}
```


---
# 4. PATCH Method

Used to update only specific fields.

Request

```http
PATCH /users/1
```

Body

```json
{
    "age": 25
}
```

Only the `age` field changes.


---
# 5. DELETE Method

Deletes a resource.

Request

```http
